extendedInfo.description: Are You Emo? How do you know for sure?Emo stands for "Emotional" and while it originally referred to a very specific kind of emotionally charged punk rock music, it has come to stand for a generation of young people who wear their tortured hearts on their tattered sleeves.Find out today if you're Emo by download this fun application.
